{"tid":749920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉鑾雄(大劉) 請返回澳門服刑 [5年3個月]","createTime":"2018-07-20T12:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T16:55:29.000Z","uid":104793,"like":210,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"39a8616b399d61d770496c8d341b4a8536b1a0a9","tid":749920,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"華人置業前主席劉鑾雄及本港商人羅傑承，因涉嫌以2000萬元賄賂歐文龍，以獲取澳門樓盤「御海‧南灣」5幅土地批給的案件，被澳門初級法院判<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">行賄及洗黑錢罪成，各判囚5年3個月</span></span>。澳門終審法院院長辦公室今(9日)發稿表示，中級法院駁回劉鑾雄的再審上訴，指其提出的證據顯然不滿足再審要求。有澳門法律界人士指，法院只會在發現極有力的新證據下，才有機會批准重審，直言劉鑾雄成功重審案件的機會「近乎零」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180109/mobile/bkn-20180109180753913-0109_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180109%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180109180753913-0109_00822_001.html&d=3rBK0zhC1nPZNeBCr%2Byu%2Bm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=240629e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180109/mobile/bkn-20180109180753913-0109_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5129658a15dcc00cf37f6e0fb1e6300ee0d902d0","tid":749920,"uid":34103,"like":17,"dislike":104,"score":-87,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff2897b82d7ba0d43ee75710c6f4fdf43d03fa0b","tid":749920,"uid":104793,"like":259,"dislike":3,"score":256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:18:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">在逃通輯犯<br />\n劉鑾雄<br />\n刑期: 5年3個月<br />\n<br />\n速速服刑<br />\n返去坐監！</span></span>"},{"pid":"991c33a73f9333f62e075eb2ea043b200dc47ad8","tid":749920,"uid":34103,"like":14,"dislike":102,"score":-88,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8d590e69391ef9e4715f4a4c0068232630c1469","tid":749920,"uid":71748,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"強烈要求特區政府同澳門簽引渡條約<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma